./findings/convergences/2026-05-26-can-first-break-mechanism-be-coded-independently-from-residue-policy-and-institut.md:9:Transformative paths should be compared by entry grammar: incapacity diagnosis, minimum participation threshold, break mechanism when threshold entry is denied, and residue policy after ordinary agency is negated.
